comments: Horton-Tucker (LAL) moves into Mitchell's (UTA) path and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
James (LAL) initiates contact to Conley's (UTA) arm/body and affects his SQBR as he goes to the basket.
O'Neale (UTA) and James (LAL) engage and disengage off ball and the contact is incidental.
Monk (LAL) legally contests Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Replay review of the foul on O'Neale (UTA) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed successful.  O'Neale does not initiate any illegal contact while defending James (LAL).
Gobert (UTA) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
Westbrook (LAL) has his off-arm placed against Conley (UTA) and as he stops short, Conley's momentum carries him forward. Westbrook does not dislodge Conley from his defensive position.
Reaves (LAL) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and any contact with Bogdanovic's (UTA) arm is marginal as he continues his drive.
Conley (UTA) commits a take foul on Westbrook (LAL).
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Westbrook (LAL).
